name: Chloe Pendant
description:
Chloe is the latest design to join the Sonobe Collection, a series of hand-folded origami pendants. The design is made using 70 squares of paper, each one carefully folded and joined together by hand. The design is named after a childhood friend who was the first one to own this design. This design is a limited edition and numbers are limited.

The lamp is hand-made in London by the designer, Kyla McCallum. It is made using paper from GF Smith, fitted with a white coated lampshade ring and 3 way continental fitting, with a UK reducer. The design is available in one size and includes a white or black pendant set with a 1m cable drop. Please let me know your colour preference for the pendant set at the checkout.

Size : H390 Ø510 mm

Dimensions are approximate.

Delivery: Orders are currently dispatched within 4 days. To guarantee delivery before Christmas please place your order by 10th December.

Thank you!
